From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: radhevrishi <radhev.232@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 8 May 2026 14:00:00 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] feat: Forward-outlook composite + Promoter Trust + PDF export

Combined patch (14 + 17) — squashed because 14 never reached origin/main
and 17 builds on it.

A. FORWARD-OUTLOOK INTO FUNDAMENTAL SCORE COMPOSITE
   Forward score (from concall extraction) is now the 6th component in
   the FundamentalScore composite alongside growth/margin/WC/promoter/
   cash. Weights when concall present:
     growth 22% · margin 20% · WC 12% · promoter 10% · cash 11% · forward 25%
   Without concall, original 30/25/15/15/15 unchanged.
   - Direction tilts: forward >=75 + composite >=50 -> 'improving'
   - Verdict tier shift: forward >=80 bumps verdict up one tier;
     forward <=25 bumps down. Pinned at extremes.

B. PROMOTER TRUST SCORE
   New 0-100 governance composite:
     Stability 40% · Pledge 30% · Consistency 15% · Institutional 15%
   Renders as saffron-bordered card above the Promoter Holding tiles
   with score, grade (A-F), verdict, and 4-input breakdown.
   - Wired into VERDICT TIER SHIFT — Trust <=30 demotes verdict one tier
   - Pledge defaults to 60 when not reported (free-tier Screener limitation)

C. INSTITUTIONAL PDF EXPORT
   New 'PDF' button next to Copy summary / New analysis. Multi-page A4
   institutional report via lazy-imported jsPDF + autotable:
   header / verdict / latest quarter / fundamental health composite /
   promoter trust breakdown / 8Q trend / concall insights / working
   capital + holdings / sector KPIs / themes / TTM ratios / footer.
   Filename: {TICKER}_{QUARTER}_institutional.pdf

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
